OL,3,CHow could the Senedd reform affect you?
OL,5,FPlans to change the size of the and
OL,6,Fthe way that it's elected reach a
OL,7,Fcrucial stage today (Tuesday 5th
OL,8,FMarch) with a marathon session of
OL,9,Fdebating and voting.
OL,11,FThe , with support from , is proposing
OL,12,Fa series of changes which will see the
OL,13,Fnumber of members increase from 60 to
OL,14,F96 and a new voting system introduced
OL,15,Fbased on new multi-member super-
OL,16,Fconstituencies along with other
OL,17,Fchanges to the system.
