OL,3,CHow could the Senedd reform affect you?
OL,5,FThe voting system has met with
OL,6,Fopposition from within and Plaid Cymru
OL,7,Fwhile the whole project has been
OL,8,Fcriticised by the as an expensive
OL,9,F"vanity project."
OL,11,FAt the moment there are 60 Senedd
OL,12,FMembers or MSs. If these changes go
OL,13,Fthrough, that number would increase to
OL,14,F96.
OL,16,FSupporters say that more are needed
OL,17,Fbecause the Welsh Parliament has more
OL,18,Flaw-making power than when it was
OL,19,Ffirst created and the Welsh Government
OL,20,Fneeds more scrutiny. Opponents say
OL,21,Fit's a waste of money creating more .
