OL,3,CHow could the Senedd reform affect you?
OL,5,FAnd the way they're elected would
OL,6,Fchange. Currently we choose 40 from
OL,7,Fconstituencies and 20 from a "top-up"
OL,8,Flist. The new system would see 16 new
OL,9,F"super constituencies" each with SIX
OL,10,FSenedd members.
OL,12,FYou wouldn't vote for an individual,
OL,13,Fyou'd vote for a political party and
OL,14,Fthe winners would be chosen from lists
OL,15,Fthat the parties provide.
OL,17,FSupporters say that's fairer and would
OL,18,Freflect the votes all parties won.
OL,19,FOpponents say it would destroy the
OL,20,Flink between voters and the person
OL,21,Frepresenting them.
