OL,3,CHow could the Senedd reform affect you?
OL,5,FThere are other changes too, such as
OL,6,Freducing the time between Senedd
OL,7,Felections from five years to four and
OL,8,Frequiring that anyone wanting to
OL,9,Fbecome a Senedd Member must live here
OL,10,Fin Wales.
OL,12,FFrom this afternoon, MSs will discuss
OL,13,Fthe legislation introducing the
OL,14,Fchanges, the Senedd Cymru (Members and
OL,15,FElections) Bill in an unusual way
OL,16,Fknown as a "Committee of the Whole
OL,17,FSenedd."
