OL,3,CHow could the Senedd reform affect you?
OL,5,FJust as happens in the UK Parliament,
OL,6,Fevery bill in the Welsh Parliament
OL,7,Fgoes through a Committee Stage, where
OL,8,Fa small number of members comb through
OL,9,Fthe legislation and suggest ways that
OL,10,Fit can be altered through amendments.
OL,12,FIn this case, every one of the 60
OL,13,Fmembers will take part in the
OL,14,FCommittee Stage which will take place
OL,15,Fin the Senedd Chamber instead of a
OL,16,Fcommittee room.
