OL,3,CHow could the Senedd reform affect you?
OL,5,FThey'll begin at 3.30pm after the
OL,6,Fusual Welsh Government question times
OL,7,Fand continue until 9.30pm before doing
OL,8,Fthe same tomorrow. They'll be debating
OL,9,Fand voting on 126 amendments, giving
OL,10,Fyou some idea of how controversial
OL,11,Fthis legislation is and how much focus
OL,12,Fthere is on it.
OL,14,FIt's estimated that the total cost of
OL,15,Fall the changes over an 8-year period
OL,16,Fwould be between #100m and #120m.
