OL,3,CHow could the Senedd reform affect you?
OL,5,FThe Conservatives have criticised the
OL,6,Fwhole project as a waste of money.
OL,7,FShadow Constitution Minister Darren
OL,8,FMillar said that "The Senedd Reform
OL,9,FBill is another pet project from
OL,10,FLabour and Plaid Cymru that is wasting
OL,11,F#120 million of taxpayers' money on
OL,12,Fmore politicians when what we really
OL,13,Fneed are more doctors, nurses,
OL,14,Fdentists and teachers.
OL,16,F"Welsh Government Ministers should be
OL,17,Ffocused on tackling the real
OL,18,Fpriorities of the people of Wales, not
OL,19,Fjob creation schemes for politicians.
