OL,3,CHow could the Senedd reform affect you?
OL,5,F"The Welsh Conservatives will continue
OL,6,Fto oppose these unnecessary proposals
OL,7,Fand have tabled dozens of amendments
OL,8,Fto this Bill, including a requirement
OL,9,Ffor any increase in the size of the
OL,10,FSenedd and the way that Members of the
OL,11,FWelsh Parliament are elected, to be
OL,12,Fsubject to a referendum before they
OL,13,Fcan be implemented."
OL,15,FOn the other side of the debate, Plaid
OL,16,FCymru will argue that the changes will
OL,17,F"place Welsh democracy on firmer
OL,18,Ffoundations."
