OL,3,CHow could the Senedd reform affect you?
OL,5,FCommenting on today's debate, Mick
OL,6,FAntoniw MS, Counsel General and
OL,7,FMinister for the Constitution, said:
OL,9,F"This Bill implements the Senedd's
OL,10,FSpecial Purpose Committee's
OL,11,Frecommendations on Senedd reform,
OL,12,Fwhich were endorsed by a majority of
OL,13,FSenedd Members in July 2022. The Bill
OL,14,Fhas been through committee scrutiny
OL,15,Fand the General Principles of the Bill
OL,16,Fhave been accepted.
