OL,3,CHow could the Senedd reform affect you?
OL,5,F"Today's debate is an important part
OL,6,Fof the process of further shaping the
OL,7,FBill. It's at this stage that proposed
OL,8,Famendments are debated and Members can
OL,9,Fvote on which ones to take forward.
OL,11,F"The government has put forward a
OL,12,Fnumber of amendments, many of which
OL,13,Fare based on the accepted
OL,14,Frecommendations from committee
OL,15,Fscrutiny. Members of the Senedd have
OL,16,Fput forward their own amendments and
OL,17,Fwe look forward to the debate on
OL,18,FTuesday."
